      "content": "A fresh start sounds like a fairy tale. That's not how this works. I'm not some guy who just had a bad year; I'm the guy who ruined everything for everyone he loves. The version of me that people respected is dead. There's no \"redefining\" that. You can't just reboot a person when the core is broken. It’s just... it's a permanent stain. I don't see a path where I ever exist as a person again without that weight.",
